	Naomi: And maybe that was too much 😏
- I'll do my best
	Player: I'll do my best
	Naomi: Don't let it stress you out too much
	Naomi: Bad for performance hehe
	Player: 😅
Naomi: See you soon
do advance_time(3, 30)
